{"id": 1242, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的工作给你带来了哪些特别的生活习惯？", "description": "本来以为跟医生处对象能被照顾的特别好，结果不管生啥病 ta 都会说“啊没啥大问题过段时间自己就好了”。一种别致的“职业病”。", "record_count": 3269, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160924112617uw1yXC05tjmElbMQ.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-27T03:03:22Z", "options": [{"id": 119668, "content": "工作太累导致生活能懒就懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 502, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708510}, {"id": 119808, "content": "作为文案，一看到广告就想校稿", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774534}, {"id": 119809, "content": "酒店从业者：什么态度！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430995}, {"id": 134402, "content": "提防各路撒比", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804638}, {"id": 119810, "content": "晚睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 121346, "content": "即使没有上学，也会在六点多醒来?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 560626}, {"id": 119811, "content": "啦啦啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 45771}, {"id": 121091, "content": "设计师，进商场和酒店先去看厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733947}, {"id": 128515, "content": "医生，你还是找专科看看吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308249}, {"id": 128516, "content": "医生，你还是找专科看看吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 308249}, {"id": 119814, "content": "谨慎", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767995}, {"id": 128262, "content": "哪里能画画到哪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813782}, {"id": 163847, "content": "师范生，对错别字不能忍受？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 119815, "content": "经常点鼠标，右手食指没事就喜欢点两下～", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760416}, {"id": 119818, "content": "程序员，一步小心钻进去了不能自拔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774555}, {"id": 128266, "content": "电话一响，紧张了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813875}, {"id": 120075, "content": "仿佛风格", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726194}, {"id": 121611, "content": "今年有假吗？   春节放多久？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783236}, {"id": 119820, "content": "创业团队什么都干，看到什么都想插一脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729185}, {"id": 120076, "content": "哈哈哈\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726194}, {"id": 119821, "content": "军事翻译... 一看到飞机大炮武器就自动翻译成英文～～～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774559}, {"id": 119822, "content": "喜欢观察周围的人，安全意识增强", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774560}, {"id": 119823, "content": "习惯晚睡早起，习惯熬夜，习惯被人误解", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774560}, {"id": 119824, "content": "对时间变得很敏感", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770379}, {"id": 119825, "content": "学地质的。看到石头就想给它命名说出它的成分。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774575}, {"id": 119826, "content": "你的这个产品备案了吗，跟备案信息一致吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478923}, {"id": 119827, "content": "午睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771629}, {"id": 121363, "content": "服务业导致对其他地方的服务不满", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780556}, {"id": 119828, "content": "工作太单调，导致工作来了都不记得有工资这回事", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336870}, {"id": 119829, "content": "强迫症，完美主义", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751188}, {"id": 124438, "content": "教师，下课不想说话；看到一些视频和新闻会想到能不能用到上课的ppt上面。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681827}, {"id": 119831, "content": "冷冻水产品业务，介个是冻的  内个是新鲜的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769112}, {"id": 120087, "content": "看书并独立思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456428}, {"id": 119832, "content": "审计狗，干什么都要留下证据…", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774255}, {"id": 120600, "content": "赚幼儿园家长的钱，结果走到哪看见小孩都觉得是一堆堆的人民币", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226639}, {"id": 119833, "content": "学生 干什么都像在写作业 做什么都像是应付差事", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 537828}, {"id": 119834, "content": "看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769442}, {"id": 120346, "content": "有字的地方都会看看，哪怕是张传单", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776840}, {"id": 129818, "content": "爱洗手了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816537}, {"id": 119835, "content": "只要一下班，我连去卫生间都懒的去", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759161}, {"id": 119836, "content": "打完辩论问别人问题都是：请问对方辩友对xxx是承认还是不承认？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733854}, {"id": 119837, "content": "咖啡师。每天吃早饭；轻度强迫症，所有器具必须摆放整齐，用过的一切都必须清理整洁… 对谁都很nice～越来越热爱生活 没事就逛馆子找好喝的咖啡，与同好争高低也是蛮有意思的事。", "image": "img/option/option/20160927172629SQpNJbf6v7hB243L.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648396}, {"id": 120093, "content": "洁癖 城市处处是细菌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775820}, {"id": 119838, "content": "听力下降造成在家看电视声音特大而被老婆打", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511093}, {"id": 119839, "content": "厨师.闻到味或者看到